{"_path":"/maps/_ai/evaluation/observability","_dir":"evaluation","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Observability","description":"LLM 可观测性平台与工具，包括 LangSmith、Phoenix、Langfuse 等追踪、评估和监控方案。","original_path":"_ai/observability.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"可观测性-observability"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可观测性 (Observability)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"langsmithlangchain-生态追踪平台"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith：LangChain 生态追踪平台"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith 是 LangChain 官方的可观测性平台，与 LangChain 生态深度集成。提供调用链可视化、错误定位与重放、批量测试评估、生产指标仪表盘。2025 年推出 LangSmith Fetch CLI 工具，可直接在终端和 IDE 中调试 Agent 追踪数据。适合已使用 LangChain 构建应用的团队，但部分功能需付费，不支持自托管。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://smith.langchain.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.langchain.com/introducing-langsmith-fetch/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith Fetch 发布"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.langchain.com/debugging-deep-agents-with-langsmith/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Deep Agents 调试指南"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"phoenix开源-llm-可观测性平台"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Phoenix：开源 LLM 可观测性平台"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Phoenix 由 Arize AI 开发，是完全开源的 LLM 可观测性解决方案。基于 OpenTelemetry 标准实现框架无关的追踪，提供 RAG 检索质量可视化、Embedding 向量空间探索、内置 Evals 评估库。支持自托管，与 MLflow 等 MLOps 工具集成良好，是企业级可观测性的首选开源方案。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/Arize-ai/phoenix","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Phoenix GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://phoenix.arize.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Phoenix 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://arize.com/docs/phoenix/evaluation/llm-evals","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM Evals 库"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"langfuse开源可观测性新选择"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Langfuse：开源可观测性新选择"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Langfuse 是 2025 年快速崛起的开源 LLM 可观测性平台，提供 Traces 追踪、Evals 评估、Prompt 管理、Metrics 指标分析。支持 OpenAI、LangChain、LlamaIndex、LiteLLM 等 10+ 集成，采用 OpenTelemetry 标准。作为完全开源的欧洲产品，是重视数据主权团队的理想选择。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://langfuse.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Langfuse 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://langfuse.com/wrapped","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Langfuse Wrapped 2025"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"opentelemetry开放追踪标准"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenTelemetry：开放追踪标准"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenTelemetry 成为 LLM 可观测性的事实标准，提供与框架无关的 instrumentation 能力。Traceloop (OpenLLMetry) 是基于 OpenTelemetry 的 SDK，实现 LLM 应用的统一追踪和指标采集。采用开放标准可避免 vendor lock-in，实现跨平台数据兼容。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/traceloop/openllmetry","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenLLMetry GitHub"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://opentelemetry.io/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"OpenTelemetry 官网"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"工具选型指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工具选型指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith 适合 LangChain 生态用户，功能完善但需付费；Phoenix 适合需要自托管和 RAG 分析的团队，完全开源；Langfuse 适合重视数据主权和 Prompt 管理的场景；OpenTelemetry 方案适合追求开放标准和技术自主的团队。实际部署中，开发阶段可用 LangSmith 快速上手，生产环境考虑 Phoenix 或 Langfuse 自托管以控制成本和数据安全。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.firecrawl.dev/blog/best-llm-observability-tools","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2025 LLM 可观测性工具榜单"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://medium.com/@aunraza021/langsmith-vs-phoenix-by-arize-ai-choosing-the-right-tool-for-llm-observability-0b4c2f21c077","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LangSmith vs Phoenix 对比"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"langsmithlangchain-生态追踪平台","depth":2,"text":"LangSmith：LangChain 生态追踪平台"},{"id":"phoenix开源-llm-可观测性平台","depth":2,"text":"Phoenix：开源 LLM 可观测性平台"},{"id":"langfuse开源可观测性新选择","depth":2,"text":"Langfuse：开源可观测性新选择"},{"id":"opentelemetry开放追踪标准","depth":2,"text":"OpenTelemetry：开放追踪标准"},{"id":"工具选型指南","depth":2,"text":"工具选型指南"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:evaluation:observability.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/evaluation/observability.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/evaluation/observability","_extension":"md"}